      </img>      
    </div>
    <div class="introduction">
      <h1 class="title">Welcom to Ejun Park's profile webpage</h1>
      <div class="description">
        <h3 class="hello"> Hello, I am Ejun, a student who wants to be a programmer. I started to study programming with C and now I can do much more things. If you'de like to know more about me, check this website.</h3>
